 {"id":"bd-2n73.3","title":"Tool detection vNext (manifest-driven + new CLIs)","description":"Upgrade agent/tool detection to use ACFS manifest and cover new CLIs/utilities (ms, wa, pt, rch, giil, csctf, xf, toon, rano, mdwb, s2p, rust_proxy, aadc, caam, slb, dcg, ubs, etc.). Include version, auth, robot capability checks, and explicit detection of MCP servers. Add deterministic test fixtures for PATH probing and auth/permission errors. Success: /agents/detected returns full, accurate tool inventory for the current machine.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:28.136243746Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T19:26:33.839605589Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:28.136243746Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:53.600533426Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:34.107278206Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:43.801395043Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2n73.4","title":"Gateway tool registry expansion (robot/TOON/MCP metadata)","description":"Extend tool registry schemas to capture robot mode flags, JSON/JSONL/TOON output formats, MCP server availability, and install/verify commands from ACFS. This enables consistent UI labeling and API feature flags (e.g., ubs TOON output, dcg robot, ms MCP). Success: registry fully describes each tool's capabilities and is consumed by detection + UI.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:36.701337569Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T18:40:12.986112596Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.4","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:36.701337569Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.4","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:40:01.486234994Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.4","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:40:12.985487027Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2n73.5","title":"New tool service clients (ms/wa/pt/rch/giil/csctf/xf/toon/etc)","description":"Add/expand gateway services and flywheel-clients wrappers for new tools in ACFS: meta_skill (ms) MCP + CLI, wezterm_automata (wa) robot, process_triage (pt) robot, remote_compilation_helper (rch) JSON, giil/csctf utilities, xf archive search, toon format helpers, and any newly installed utilities. Define typed request/response models, standardized error mapping, and structured logging of tool invocations. Success: gateway can invoke these tools with machine-readable output and surface results via API.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:44.281038932Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T19:29:04.691754130Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:44.281038932Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:40:24.769951305Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.5","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:40:36.648689832Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
